homedir

A Puppet module to manage my personal home directory.  Inspired by:
http://vstone.eu/bootstrap-your-home-folder-puppet/

Example
-------

mkdir -p ~/.puppet/modules
git clone git://github.com/anl/puppet-homedir.git ~/.puppet/modules/homedir
puppet apply -e "include homedir"

